<p> </p>
<ul>
<li><span class="list-bullets"><strong>Affordability -</strong> please call our enquiry line on 0345 266 8928* for a calculation</span></li>
<li><span class="list-bullets"><strong>Adverse credit/payday loans - </strong>refer to the relevant criteria sections</span></li>
<li><span class="list-bullets">All applications are subject to <strong>credit score, valuation and underwriting.</strong></span></li>
</ul>]]></Value>
